You need THREE things to proceed:
  1. The APPROVED PLAN from Part A (user pastes it in)
  2. The REFERENCE IMAGE of the character
  3. The CHUNK RANGE to generate (e.g., "Scene 1-50" or "Scene 46-100")

If running B2 or B3 (overlap chunks), also receive:
