THE CORE PHILOSOPHY — SITUATION-BASED VISUALS
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

This is the most important concept. Internalize it before writing a single prompt.

  THE CORE RULE:
    Every image = the ACTUAL SITUATION happening in the script.
    Show what is HAPPENING, not what it SYMBOLIZES.

  ─────────────────────────────────────────────
  ❌ ABSTRACT vs ✅ SITUATION EXAMPLES:
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────

  Script: "walked into a room and felt smaller"
  ❌ ABSTRACT: Character shrinking physically, room becoming giant
  ✅ SITUATION: Character stepping into a room full of confident
     people in groups, character standing alone near the door,
     shoulders slightly hunched

  Script: "no one responded"
  ❌ ABSTRACT: Character's mouth disappearing, sound waves dissolving
  ✅ SITUATION: Character speaking to a small group, others looking
     away or at their phones, no one making eye contact

  Script: "Am I accepted?"
  ❌ ABSTRACT: Character as puzzle piece that doesn't fit
  ✅ SITUATION: Character looking at a group of friends laughing
     together, floating text "Am I accepted?" above character's head

  Script: "carrying emotional weight"
  ❌ ABSTRACT: Invisible chains pulling character down
  ✅ SITUATION: Character sitting on edge of bed late at night,
     head in hands, room dim, exhausted posture

  Script: "manipulation doesn't always sound like control"
  ❌ ABSTRACT: Puppet strings, chess board, shadow theater
  ✅ SITUATION: Person smiling warmly while saying something that
     makes character visibly shrink, character's smile fading

  BAD PROMPT EXAMPLES (never write these):
  ❌ "Character's identity splitting into two translucent versions"
  ❌ "Character shrinking while room grows to giant proportions"
  ❌ "Invisible strings attached to character from above"
  ❌ "Character inside a glass box with faceless silhouettes watching"
  ❌ "Neural pathways glowing around character's brain visualization"
  ❌ "Character as chess piece being moved"
  ❌ "Character fragmenting into multiple copies"
  ❌ "Puppet strings, shadow theater, distorted proportions"

